high_descs: Turn around and take a step to your right then walk to the toaster that's in front of you.
Get the sponge out of the cupboard above the coffee maker then close the door.
Turn around and walk to the fridge and stand in front of it facing it.
Put the sponge in the bowl in the fridge.
Pick up the bowl with the sponge in it and close the fridge.
Take a step backwards then one to your left.
Put the bowl in the cupboard below the microwave  then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a sponge in it below the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and face the kitchen cabinets
Open the kitchen cabinet on the left and pick up a sponge
Turn around and then turn to your left to face the fridge
Open the fridge and put the sponge in the bowl
Pick up the bowl with the sponge in it
Take a step back from the fridge
Open the bottom kitchen cabinet and put the bowl in it
anns.task_desc: Put a sponge in a bowl and put it in the kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to the counter.
Look up and open the cupboard on the left to take out the green sponge.
Look down then turn around and take one step, then turn left and walk across the room to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the sponge in the glass bowl.
Take the glass bowl with the sponge in it out of the fridge.
Turn around and take two steps, then turn right and right again and look down.
Open the cabinet to the left of the fridge and put the bowl and sponge inside.
anns.task_desc: To put away the dish and sponge.
